  "title": "*Entry* Sales & Business Development (Mentorship, Fresh Grads Welcome)",
  "description": "<p><strong>💼 Sales &amp; Business Development - </strong><em>Immediate Start / Office Hours / Fixed Schedule / No-Exp Needed! </em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Looking to kickstart your career in sales and business development? Join our dynamic team where growth is real, support is constant, and every win is celebrated!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We’re on the lookout for motivated individuals to help us build meaningful partnerships and drive business success. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong><br>\n🔹 Identify and reach out to potential corporate customers<br>\n🔹 Present solutions and build long-term customer relationships<br>\n🔹 Support end-to-end sales processes from pitch to close<br>\n🔹 Collaborate with the team to hit targets<br>\n🔹 Attend trainings and client conventions </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong><br>\n✅ Full mentorship and on-the-job training<br>\n✅ Supportive team with a growth-focused environment<br>\n✅ Clear career path with advancement opportunities<br>\n✅ Fun, energetic work culture. <br>\n✅ Performance incentives and recognition</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ready? <u><strong>JOIN US NOW!!</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>",
